            "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EHere are some of the commands you can use with NVDA to make your testing faster and easier. If you are not familiar with the NVDA key, please read the \u003Ca target=\u0022\u0022 data-router-slot=\u0022disabled\u0022 href=\u0022/{localLink:8cba3b31-bfbe-4a67-beb0-60dd7728d54c}\u0022 title=\u0022NVDA\u0022 type=\u0022document\u0022\u003ENVDA quick start\u003C/a\u003E first.\u003C/p\u003E"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
